<h3>Sruti Kendra has different wings </h3>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Sruti Balakendra - for children upto 12 years </li>
                        <li>Sruti Yuvakendra - for youth upto 20 years </li>
                        <li>Sruti Sreekendra - for developing and empowering women</li>
                        <li>Sruti Shikshakendra - for elders</li>
                        <li>Sruti Sevakendra - for service to less privileged in Society.</li>
                    </ol>
                    <p>The childrenâ€™s wing (Balakendra) and youth wing (Yuvakendra) are two of the most important movements because children and youth are the change agents in society and developing the correct value system and developing their all round leadership skills are very important for a great Society and Nation. </p>
